data.title: Community Bible Church Home Page
data.text:
Gather With Us

We would love to have you join us for worship. CBC has many services from which you can choose. Whether you are an early riser or wake up at noon, there is a service for you.

Latest Message

Holy Habits | Can You Hear Me Now?

Pastor Ed Newton

"Now Jesus was praying in a certain place, and when he finished, one of his disciples said to him, “Lord, teach us to pray...” Luke 11:1

The Person of God has to become more important than our Petitions to God.

I am Not Ashamed

Baptism

Baptism is an act of obedience of your decision to follow Jesus. If you have made this decision, we have baptism the last weekend of each month.

Learn More
